
<p>
    Hi <strong>@Model.SecurityConsultantName,</strong>
</p>


<p>
    For <strong>@Model.TenantName</strong> tenancy, one or more risks are raised for various business units and the details are mentioned below:

    <ol>
        @foreach (var risksPerBU in Model.RisksPerBusinessUnits)
        {

            <li>@risksPerBU.CompanyName - <span> @string.Format("Count: ({0})", @risksPerBU.NumberOfRisks) </span> </li>
        }
    </ol>
</p>

<p>
    The number of risks for each Business Unit that requires 'Peer review' from your end is mentioned as well. Hence, kindly log in and perform the required actions.
    <ol>
        @foreach (var risksPerEng in Model.RisksPerEngagements)
        {

            <li>@risksPerEng.EngagementName</li>
        }
    </ol>
</p>


<p>
    <strong>Hints</strong>
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Don't share login credentials with other people - you can delegate the questionnaire to others after login.</li>
    <li>Continue editing the answers until you are satisfied to submit the completed questionnaire to the security assessor.</li>
    <li>After submitting your completed answers, we may need to contact you to discuss further.</li>
    <li>For assistance, contact the security consultant or access Help (link to external site).</li>
</ul>

